achievement.title: Earth, Wind & Fire (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat Archavon the Stone Watcher, Emalon the Storm Watcher, and Koralon the Flame Watcher within 60 seconds of each other in 10-player mode.

achievement.title: Heroic: The Frostwing Halls (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat the bosses of The Frostwing Halls in Icecrown Citadel in 10-player Heroic mode.

achievement.title: Portal Jockey (10 player)
achievement.description: Enter every portal spawned by Valithria Dreamwalker before healing her to full health in 10-player mode.

achievement.title: Heroic: The Crimson Hall (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat the bosses of The Crimson Hall in Icecrown Citadel in 10-player Heroic mode.

achievement.title: The Orb Whisperer (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat the Blood Council without anyone in the raid taking more than 23,000 spell damage in a single hit in 10-player mode.

achievement.title: Heroic: The Plagueworks (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat the bosses of The Plagueworks in Icecrown Citadel in 10-player Heroic mode.

achievement.title: Heroic: Storming the Citadel (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat the first four bosses in Icecrown Citadel in 10-player Heroic mode.

criteria.description: Claim victory in the Gunship Battle

achievement.title: Full House (10 player)
achievement.description: Defeat Lady Deathwhisper with at least five different types of Cultists active at the time of her demise in 10-player mode.

achievement.title: So Grossly Incandescent
achievement.description: Defeat Rukhmar in Spires of Arak.

Headed South
achievement.description: Defeat Siamat, Lord of the South Wind, with 3 stacks of Lightning Charge in Lost City of the Tol'vir on Heroic Difficulty.

achievement.description: Defeat all of the Pet Tamers in Kalimdor listed below.

achievement.title: You're Just Making It WORSE!
achievement.description: Defeat Millificent Manastorm after she becomes very cross with you in Assault on Violet Hold on Mythic difficulty.
